    "possibleUpdate": false,
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Holy Devastator:</strong>&nbsp;In the hands of any character other than a paladin, this sword performs as a +<em>3 holy longsword</em>. In the hands of a paladin, this weapon functions as a +<em>7 longsword of holy power</em>&nbsp;and grants a +5 sacred bonus on the wielder's saving throws against spells with the evil descriptor or spells cast by evil characters. If the paladin wielder smites evil with the&nbsp;<em>holy devastator</em>, he or she adds twice his or her paladin level to damage (rather than his or her paladin level).</p>\n<p><em>Caster Level:</em>&nbsp;23rd;&nbsp;<em>Prerequisites:</em>&nbsp;Craft Magic Arms and Armor, Craft Epic Magic Arms and Armor,&nbsp;<em>holy aura</em>,&nbsp;<em>holy smite</em>,&nbsp;<em>holy word; Market Price:</em>&nbsp;4,620,315 gp;&nbsp;<em>Cost to Create:</em>&nbsp;2,310,315 gp + 56,200 XP.</p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": "<p>This classic, straight blade is the weapon of knighthood and valor. It is a favorite weapon of many paladins.</p>"
    },
